<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<section class="page-header">
  <span class="eyebrow">Services</span>
  <h1 class="display">Everything it takes<br>to grow.</h1>
  <p class="lede">Four services, one accountable team. We fix how your brand shows up, get you found across search and AI, build automation and AI into your operations, and give you the strategy to tie it all together.</p>
</section>

<section class="container" style="padding:0 24px 30px;">
  <div class="grid-seam grid-seam--auto-sm">
    <a href="#brand" style="background:var(--card);padding:20px 22px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:baseline;">
      <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--accent);">01</span><span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Branding &amp; visibility</span>
    </a>
    <a href="#ai-search" style="background:var(--card);padding:20px 22px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:baseline;">
      <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--accent);">02</span><span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Get found in AI search</span>
    </a>
    <a href="#automation" style="background:var(--card);padding:20px 22px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:baseline;">
      <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--accent);">03</span><span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Automation &amp; AI</span>
    </a>
    <a href="#consulting" style="background:var(--card);padding:20px 22px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:baseline;">
      <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--accent);">04</span><span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Consulting</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="brand" class="section section--top-border">
  <div class="container" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:56px;align-items:start;">
    <div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--text-faint);margin-bottom:14px;">01 &middot; Foundations</div>
      <h2 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(28px,3.6vw,40px);line-height:1.08;margin-bottom:18px;">Fix your branding &amp; online visibility</h2>
      <p class="body-text" style="color:var(--text-muted);">If your brand looks smaller than you are, or you&rsquo;re hard to find and easy to distrust, nothing else works as hard as it should. We sharpen your identity and clean up your presence everywhere buyers look &mdash; so you look the part on first impression.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-seam" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;">
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Brand identity &amp; messaging</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">A clear wordmark, voice, and story so you look and sound like one company.</div></div>
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Website &amp; profile cleanup</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">A consistent, credible presence across your site, Google Business, and social.</div></div>
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Reputation &amp; findability</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">Close the gaps that make you hard to find &mdash; or easy to overlook.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="ai-search" class="section section--top-border">
  <div class="container" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:56px;align-items:start;">
    <div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--text-faint);margin-bottom:14px;">02 &middot; GEO &middot; AEO &middot; SEO</div>
      <h2 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(28px,3.6vw,40px);line-height:1.08;margin-bottom:18px;">Get found in AI search</h2>
      <p class="body-text" style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:18px;">Buyers now ask AI and act on a single answer. There&rsquo;s no page two. We get you cited and recommended across ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, Perplexity, Claude, Gemini, Grok, and Copilot &mdash; and keep you ranking in Google while we do it.</p>
      <a href="/process" class="btn-link">See how the method works &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-seam" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;">
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Generative Engine Optimization (GEO)</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">Shape how AI models talk about and recommend your brand across prompts.</div></div>
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">Structure content, schema, and entities so engines can extract and cite you.</div></div>
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">The fundamentals that keep you ranking &mdash; and feed the trust AI relies on.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="automation" class="section section--top-border">
  <div class="container" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:56px;align-items:start;">
    <div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--text-faint);margin-bottom:14px;">03 &middot; Build</div>
      <h2 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(28px,3.6vw,40px);line-height:1.08;margin-bottom:18px;">Custom automation &amp; AI integration</h2>
      <p class="body-text" style="color:var(--text-muted);">The busywork eating your team&rsquo;s hours can be automated &mdash; and AI can do far more than write copy. We connect your tools, build custom workflows, and integrate AI where it earns its keep, so you move faster and scale without adding headcount.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-seam" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;">
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Workflow automation</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">Connect your tools and kill repetitive manual work across the business.</div></div>
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Custom AI integration</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">Add AI where it matters &mdash; support, content, ops, and sales.</div></div>
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Internal tools &amp; agents</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">Lightweight software and AI agents built for how your team actually works.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="consulting" class="section section--top-border">
  <div class="container" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:56px;align-items:start;">
    <div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--text-faint);margin-bottom:14px;">04 &middot; Direction</div>
      <h2 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(28px,3.6vw,40px);line-height:1.08;margin-bottom:18px;">Consulting</h2>
      <p class="body-text" style="color:var(--text-muted);">Sometimes you don&rsquo;t need us to do it &mdash; you need a straight answer on what to do next. Get clear strategy and hands-on guidance to decide what to fix, what to build, and where growth actually comes from.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-seam" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;">
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Strategy &amp; roadmap</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">Where to focus first, and what it takes to win in your market.</div></div>
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Fractional guidance</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">Ongoing expert direction without the cost of a full-time hire.</div></div>
      <div style="padding:22px 26px;"><div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;">Audits &amp; training</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">Know exactly where you stand &mdash; and level up your team to keep it going.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/faq') %>

<section class="cta-band section--top-border">
  <div class="cta-band__inner">
    <h2>Not sure which you need?</h2>
    <p>That&rsquo;s what the strategy call is for. We&rsquo;ll find what&rsquo;s holding you back and map the fastest fix &mdash; no obligation.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book a strategy call</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
